{
  "stem": "14190.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were divided in different groups, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so-- maybe there were more women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The women that took care of us, I remember two-- two ladies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember the Germans talking to-- the Nazis were talking to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after a little bit, after a little bit, one lady started to cry and walked away quickly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the other one was calling her and say, gather them fast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Gather them fast, fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Don't talk to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Don't tell them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Don't tell them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, when I heard, don't tell them, then I thought that something bad is about to happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I grabbed my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, behind that building, there were some bushes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I-- I-- just like a premonition, I grabbed my sister and I hid in that-- in that little bit of bushes behind the building.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, sure enough, they were getting those kids and they're putting them into the buses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The kids, they walked willingly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were given some candies or something and walking to the buses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was watching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was watching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then the buses started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I thought that they're going to-- they're going to drive away, except they were started and going and going.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And nothing is going away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so I didn't-- I didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I stayed behind that-- behind that-- for a long time with my sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Not all the kids went to these-- to these buses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Later on, a long time afterwards, the buses drove away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
